author: Nel
title: Nel
text: No real serious problems just one concern i understand it's a job but after constantly and exactly telling seller what we were looking for seller still insisted we choose and got something completely different he didn't care of our needs just wanted to make a sell for his commission. Still a great place to shop tho with good variety and prices to fit your budget.
